title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Boeing 247D - Starting the engines
description:
If you want to give yourself a challenge starting the engines of an aircraft than give the Boeing 247D a try. This is by far the most difficult aircraft to start which makes flying even more challenging. In this video I will show you how I got them running.
